>> BEEN THAT WAY FOR YEARS.

01:54.633 --> 01:55.633
HOW HAVE YOU BEEN, APRIL?

01:55.633 --> 01:57.000
>> I'M GOOD, THANK YOU, VICTOR.

01:57.000 --> 01:58.767
>> OH, WE HAVEN'T BEEN ABLE TO

01:58.767 --> 01:59.833
