OUR FAMILIES ARE ALREADY CLOSE.

03:30.900 --> 03:32.933
HE'S SMART, SUCCESSFUL.

03:32.933 --> 03:35.367
HE IS GONNA BE A GREAT DAD.

03:35.367 --> 03:36.300
