03:44.767 --> 03:46.467
OF COURSE I LOVE HIM.

03:46.467 --> 03:49.567
>> WHO SAID ANYTHING ABOUT LOVE?

03:49.567 --> 03:52.400
OH, BOY, HERE COMES YOUR MOTHER.

03:52.400 --> 03:54.233
>> WELL, HELLO, STRANGER.

03:54.233 --> 03:55.167
>> MM.

03:55.167 --> 03:56.000
>> RAQUEL TELLS ME THAT YOU'RE

03:56.000 --> 03:57.000
DOING REAL ESTATE INSTEAD OF

03:57.000 --> 03:58.133
VIDEOS NOW.

03:58.133 --> 03:59.533
>> MM-HMM.

03:59.533 --> 04:00.800
>> I'M GLAD TO HEAR YOU'RE

04:00.800 --> 04:01.933
SHOWING HOMES INSTEAD OF YOUR

04:01.933 --> 04:04.067
GOODS.

04:04.067 --> 04:05.567
>> NICE TO SEE YOU AS WELL,

04:05.567 --> 04:06.267
EVELYN.

04:06.267 --> 04:07.800
>> I'M FINALLY GOING TO MARRY

04:07.800 --> 04:08.933
RAQUEL OFF.

04:08.933 --> 04:09.833
WHEN IS IT GOING TO BE YOUR

04:09.833 --> 04:10.500
TURN?

04:10.500 --> 04:11.267
>> I DON'T KNOW.

04:11.267 --> 04:13.100
AS HARD AS I TRY, I CAN'T SEEM

04:13.100 --> 04:14.600
TO LOVE ANY MAN THE WAY I LOVE

04:14.600 --> 04:17.433
MYSELF.

04:17.433 --> 04:18.900
>> [chuckles]

04:18.900 --> 04:20.067
I'M GOING TO GO DANCE, AND,

04:20.067 --> 04:21.133
KEISHA, RATHER THAN JOKE ABOUT

04:21.133 --> 04:23.133
HOW SINGLE YOU ARE, YOU MIGHT

04:23.133 --> 04:25.267
WANT TO TAKE ADVANTAGE OF ALL

04:25.267 --> 04:29.700
THESE ELIGIBLE MEN AROUND HERE.

04:29.700 --> 04:30.833
>> [groans]

