>> OKAY.

04:33.100 --> 04:34.500
I BETTER GO CHANGE INTO FABULOUS

04:34.500 --> 04:35.767
DRESS NUMBER TWO FOR MY FAMILY

04:35.767 --> 04:40.800
PHOTO.

04:40.800 --> 04:41.767
