06:36.733 --> 06:39.033
IT.

06:44.867 --> 06:45.700
>> YOU LOOK GORGEOUS TONIGHT,

06:45.700 --> 06:46.500
KEISHA.

06:46.500 --> 06:49.467
>> I KNOW.

06:49.467 --> 06:53.433
>> BET MALCOLM WOULD AGREE.

06:53.433 --> 06:54.133
>> THAT I WOULDN'T KNOW,

06:54.133 --> 06:57.867
AGENT LONG.

06:57.867 --> 06:59.033
BUT FOLLOWING ME AROUND WILL GET

06:59.033 --> 07:00.100
