32:24.667 --> 32:25.333
I JUST HEARD THAT YOU'RE

32:25.333 --> 32:26.400
ACTUALLY CONSIDERING GOING DOWN

32:26.400 --> 32:27.400
FOR THIS GUY.

32:27.400 --> 32:30.100
KEISHA, YOU CANNOT BE SERIOUS.

32:30.100 --> 32:30.767
>> I DON'T KNOW.

32:30.767 --> 32:31.433
CERTAIN MEN WILL MAKE US DO

32:31.433 --> 32:33.400
CRAZY THINGS.

32:33.400 --> 32:36.467
BUT, KEISHA, THIS IS YOUR LIFE.

32:36.467 --> 32:37.733
>> YEAH, BUT MALCOLM HAS A

32:37.733 --> 32:38.900
GAZILLION DOLLARS.

32:38.900 --> 32:40.200
HE CAN BUY SOLUTIONS TO HIS

32:40.200 --> 32:40.967
PROBLEMS.

32:40.967 --> 32:42.033
AND WHERE IS HE ANYWAY?

32:42.033 --> 32:43.100
WHY ISN'T HE TRYING TO GET YOU

32:43.100 --> 32:43.767
OUT OF THIS MESS?

32:43.767 --> 32:45.300
>> APRIL, I JUST GOT ARRESTED

32:45.300 --> 32:46.867
NINE HOURS AGO.

32:46.867 --> 32:48.067
I HAVEN'T CALLED HIM BECAUSE

32:48.067 --> 32:49.033
I DON'T KNOW WHERE I LEFT THAT

32:49.033 --> 32:50.633
DAMN DISPOSABLE PHONE.

32:50.633 --> 32:52.800
MAYBE I CAN GO IN AND DANCE

32:52.800 --> 32:54.667
AROUND THEIR QUESTIONS UNTIL HE

32:54.667 --> 32:56.200
AND I FIGURE SOMETHING OUT.

32:56.200 --> 32:57.000
>> KEISHA, THEY SENT

32:57.000 --> 32:58.133
MARTHA STEWART TO PRISON FOR

32:58.133 --> 32:59.200
DANCING AROUND QUESTIONS.

32:59.200 --> 33:00.200
WHAT DO YOU THINK THEY'RE GONNA

33:00.200 --> 33:03.300
DO TO YOU?

33:12.100 --> 33:13.533
>> HEY.

33:13.533 --> 33:14.800
LEONARDO.

33:14.800 --> 33:15.567
YOU'VE GOT THE PICTURES?

33:15.567 --> 33:17.500
>> WAIT TILL YOU SEE THEM.

33:17.500 --> 33:22.333
THEY'RE INCREDIBLE.

33:22.333 --> 33:27.000
>> OH.

33:27.000 --> 33:29.567
WOW.

33:29.567 --> 33:32.033
THAT'S ME?

33:32.033 --> 33:35.367
>> THERE GOES MY TUMMY AGAIN.

33:39.467 --> 33:41.767
>> THIS GIRL SEEMS SO FREE.

33:41.767 --> 33:43.367
SO HAPPY.

33:43.367 --> 33:44.933
I'VE SPENT SO MANY YEARS BEING

33:44.933 --> 33:47.167
THE GOOD DAUGHTER, THE GOOD

33:47.167 --> 33:48.367
GIRLFRIEND, THE GOOD EMPLOYEE,

33:48.367 --> 33:51.467
THAT WHO I REALLY AM HAS GOTTEN

33:51.467 --> 33:52.533
LOST.

33:52.533 --> 33:53.667
>> NOT LOST.

33:53.667 --> 33:55.700
MISPLACED PERHAPS.

33:55.700 --> 33:58.200
>> MAYBE SO.

33:58.200 --> 34:01.233
BUT AFTER THIS WEEK, I'M READY

34:01.233 --> 34:03.000
TO FIND HER.

34:03.000 --> 34:03.667
NO MATTER WHERE THE JOURNEY

34:03.667 --> 34:06.600
TAKES ME.

34:06.600 --> 34:08.600
THANK YOU, LEONARDO.

34:08.600 --> 34:13.133
>> TRULY, RAQUEL...

34:13.133 --> 34:17.500
IT WAS MY PLEASURE.

34:18.833 --> 34:20.133
>> YOU'RE LEAVING?

34:20.133 --> 34:21.467
I WAS HOPING TO SPEND MORE TIME

34:21.467 --> 34:22.200
WITH YOU.

34:22.200 --> 34:23.067
>> AND I WITH YOU.

34:23.067 --> 34:24.567
BUT YOU NEED SOME SPACE AND TIME

34:24.567 --> 34:26.333
TO FIGURE THINGS OUT.

34:26.333 --> 34:27.200
I THINK I COULD DO A STRONG LINE

34:27.200 --> 34:28.833
WITH YOU SOMEDAY.

34:28.833 --> 34:29.633
>> WHAT DOES THAT MEAN?

34:29.633 --> 34:30.500
>> IT MEANS I DON'T WANT TO BE

34:30.500 --> 34:35.067
YOUR REBOUND GUY.

34:40.167 --> 34:41.567
>> WHAT DOES THAT MEAN?

34:41.567 --> 34:43.367
>> IT MEANS MAYBE ONE DAY THE

34:43.367 --> 34:46.200
TIMING WILL BE RIGHT.

34:46.200 --> 34:51.900
>> * LET ME BE

34:51.900 --> 34:57.867
[cell phone ringing]

35:06.700 --> 35:08.900
>> HEY, BABY.

35:08.900 --> 35:10.600
>> THIS IS RAQUEL, MALCOLM.

35:10.600 --> 35:12.067
AND YOU SHOULD KNOW THAT BABY IS

35:12.067 --> 35:15.500
IN A LOT OF TROUBLE.

35:19.500 --> 35:22.333
>> SO HOW ABOUT A MOVIE?

35:22.333 --> 35:25.067
>> SOUNDS FUN.

35:25.067 --> 35:26.433
[yawns]

35:26.433 --> 35:27.300
>> JUST ADMIT IT, APRIL.

35:27.300 --> 35:28.067
YOU'RE NOT INTERESTED IN ME.

35:28.067 --> 35:28.733
>> WHAT?

35:28.733 --> 35:30.233
NO, OF COURSE I AM.

35:30.233 --> 35:30.967
>> NO, YOU'RE NOT.

35:30.967 --> 35:31.900
AND I DON'T GET WHY.

35:31.900 --> 35:34.200
I'M NICE, DECENT-LOOKING, AND I

35:34.200 --> 35:35.433
PULL IN SIX FIGURES.

35:35.433 --> 35:36.767
I DON'T UNDERSTAND WHAT MORE

35:36.767 --> 35:37.700
WOMEN WANT.

35:37.700 --> 35:38.467
AREN'T YOU ALL ULTIMATELY

35:38.467 --> 35:39.700
LOOKING FOR SOMEONE TO SETTLE

35:39.700 --> 35:40.700
DOWN WITH?

35:40.700 --> 35:42.433
>> I GUESS, AT SOME POINT.

35:42.433 --> 35:44.333
BUT, DAN, NO, WE'RE JUST IN

35:44.333 --> 35:45.567
DIFFERENT PLACES RIGHT NOW.

35:45.567 --> 35:46.733
YOU'RE LOOKING FOR YOUR NEXT

35:46.733 --> 35:47.433
WIFE.

35:47.433 --> 35:49.200
BUT THIS IS THE FIRST TIME THAT

35:49.200 --> 35:50.567
I'VE BEEN SINGLE SINCE I WAS

35:50.567 --> 35:52.000
17 YEARS OLD.

35:52.000 --> 35:54.767
I HAVE LITERALLY NEVER DATED.

35:54.767 --> 35:55.433
EVER.

35:55.433 --> 35:56.233
>> REALLY?

35:56.233 --> 35:56.967
>> REALLY.

35:56.967 --> 35:58.800
AND I THINK I JUST--I JUST WANT

35:58.800 --> 36:00.100
TO HAVE FUN.

36:00.100 --> 36:01.067
LIKE, I'M NOT READY TO BE

36:01.067 --> 36:02.633
SOMEONE'S WIFE AGAIN.

36:02.633 --> 36:03.500
>> I UNDERSTAND.

36:03.500 --> 36:04.500
YOU WANT TO BE A KID IN A SINGLE

36:04.500 --> 36:06.033
LADY'S CANDY STORE.

36:06.033 --> 36:07.467
>> I'M NOT REALLY SURE WHAT THAT

36:07.467 --> 36:09.200
MEANS, BUT YEAH.

36:09.200 --> 36:10.800
YEAH, I THINK SO.

36:10.800 --> 36:11.500
LUNCH IS ON ME.

36:11.500 --> 36:13.633
THANK YOU SO MUCH FOR HELPING ME

36:13.633 --> 36:14.967
FIGURE THIS OUT.

36:14.967 --> 36:16.167
AND GOOD LUCK FINDING HER.

36:16.167 --> 36:16.900
YOU ARE GONNA MAKE SOMEONE

36:16.900 --> 36:19.367
REALLY HAPPY.

36:19.367 --> 36:20.633
MWAH.

36:20.633 --> 36:21.633
[Jump Clubb's

36:21.633 --> 36:24.500
Let's Crash This Party]

36:24.500 --> 36:28.000
*

36:28.000 --> 36:30.600
* I FLEW OVER YOUR HOUSE

36:30.600 --> 36:31.600
>> ARE YOU SURE YOU'RE READY TO

36:31.600 --> 36:32.300
DO THIS?

36:32.300 --> 36:34.033
>> I'M GONNA HAVE TO BE, RIGHT?

36:34.033 --> 36:37.600
LOVELY TO SEE YOU, KEISHA.

36:37.600 --> 36:38.933
>> SO WHERE ARE WE HAVING THIS

36:38.933 --> 36:43.100
CONVERSATION?

36:43.100 --> 36:45.233
>> MALCOLM FRANKS.

36:45.233 --> 36:47.500
>> AGENT LONG.

36:47.500 --> 36:48.633
SO LISTEN, I'VE BEEN AWAY ON

36:48.633 --> 36:49.867
BUSINESS, AND I HEARD YOU'VE

36:49.867 --> 36:50.633
BEEN LOOKING FOR ME.

36:50.633 --> 36:52.100
I ALSO HEARD YOU'VE BEEN GIVING

36:52.100 --> 36:54.500
MY GIRL A VERY HARD TIME.

36:54.500 --> 36:55.867
WELL, NOW YOU'VE GOT ME, SO YOU

36:55.867 --> 36:57.033
CAN LET HER GO.

36:57.033 --> 36:58.067
>> NICE OF YOU TO FINALLY SHOW

36:58.067 --> 37:00.933
UP.

37:00.933 --> 37:01.700
>> DO I KNOW YOU?

37:01.700 --> 37:02.533
>> NOT YET.

37:02.533 --> 37:03.867
BUT I BELIEVE THIS CHANGES

37:03.867 --> 37:06.200
THINGS FOR MY CLIENT.

37:06.200 --> 37:09.767
LET'S GO, KEISHA.

37:09.767 --> 37:11.500
>> YOU GOT A NAME, MAN?

37:11.500 --> 37:13.867
>> SEAN.

37:13.867 --> 37:15.700
CLARK.

37:15.700 --> 37:18.500
>> MY...LAWYER.

37:23.900 --> 37:29.333
>> LET'S GO DO THIS.

37:29.333 --> 37:31.067
[Erin Barra's Magician]

37:31.067 --> 37:35.633
*

37:35.633 --> 37:36.800
>> LOOK WHAT I BOUGHT THE OTHER

37:36.800 --> 37:37.500
DAY.

37:37.500 --> 37:40.267
YOU LIKE?

37:40.267 --> 37:41.100
>> I LIKE.

37:41.100 --> 37:42.767
BUT YOUR MOM WON'T LIKE IF

37:42.767 --> 37:43.767
YOU'RE WEARING THAT TO SUNDAY

37:43.767 --> 37:44.767
DINNER.

37:44.767 --> 37:45.633
>> I'M NOT GOING TO SUNDAY

37:45.633 --> 37:46.300
DINNER.

37:46.300 --> 37:49.433
NOT TODAY, NOT ANYTIME SOON.

37:49.433 --> 37:50.900
>> GIRL, WHEN YOU REBEL, YOU

37:50.900 --> 37:52.933
JUST GO ALL THE WAY, DON'T YOU?

37:52.933 --> 37:55.933
[knock at door]

37:55.933 --> 37:58.900
>> HMM.

38:10.000 --> 38:15.700
>> HI.

38:15.700 --> 38:16.767
>> HEY.

38:16.767 --> 38:17.933
>> I CALLED YOU 50 TIMES TO

38:17.933 --> 38:19.133
APOLOGIZE, BUT YOU KEEP CHOOSING

38:19.133 --> 38:19.967
TO IGNORE ME.

38:19.967 --> 38:21.300
SO LET'S JUST TALK ABOUT IT IN

38:21.300 --> 38:23.167
THE CAR ON THE WAY.

38:23.167 --> 38:24.600
>> ON THE WAY?

38:24.600 --> 38:25.400
>> TO YOUR PARENTS' FOR SUNDAY

38:25.400 --> 38:26.267
DINNER.

38:26.267 --> 38:27.067
WE CAN SHOW EVERYBODY WE'RE

38:27.067 --> 38:28.533
TRYING TO WORK THINGS OUT.

38:28.533 --> 38:29.833
>> DINNER IS NOT AN OPTION.

38:29.833 --> 38:31.167
BUT WE DEFINITELY NEED TO TALK.

38:31.167 --> 38:34.733
LET'S TAKE A RIDE.

38:34.733 --> 38:39.033
>> * OVER FOREVER

38:39.033 --> 38:42.467
* OVER

38:42.467 --> 38:43.633
>> THAT WASN'T THE FIRST TIME

38:43.633 --> 38:45.233
YOU CHEATED, WAS IT?

38:45.233 --> 38:47.100
>> NO.

38:47.100 --> 38:48.533
>> WHY DO YOU EVEN WANT TO MARRY

38:48.533 --> 38:49.300
ME?

38:49.300 --> 38:50.333
>> ARE YOU SERIOUS?

38:50.333 --> 38:51.767
WE'VE KNOWN EACH OTHER SINCE WE

38:51.767 --> 38:53.033
WERE KIDS, AND OUR FAMILIES ARE

38:53.033 --> 38:54.133
CLOSE.

38:54.133 --> 38:55.100
WE LIKE ALL THE SAME THINGS, AND

38:55.100 --> 38:55.967
WE LOVE EACH OTHER.

38:55.967 --> 38:56.800
IT JUST MAKES SENSE.

38:56.800 --> 38:58.500
>> VICTOR, I NEED A MAN WHO CAN

38:58.500 --> 39:00.200
BARELY THINK STRAIGHT BECAUSE HE

39:00.200 --> 39:02.333
HASN'T HEARD MY VOICE ALL DAY.

39:02.333 --> 39:03.567
OR A MAN WHO CAN'T FALL ASLEEP

39:03.567 --> 39:04.967
BECAUSE I'M NOT NEXT TO HIM.

39:04.967 --> 39:07.000
I DON'T WANT LOGIC IN MY LOVE.

39:07.000 --> 39:09.533
I WANT PASSION.

39:09.533 --> 39:10.433
DON'T YOU WANT IT TOO?

39:10.433 --> 39:11.833
>> BUT I DO LOVE YOU.

39:11.833 --> 39:12.833
>> MAYBE.

39:12.833 --> 39:14.733
BUT IT'S NOT THE MARRYING KIND

39:14.733 --> 39:16.000
OF LOVE.

39:16.000 --> 39:17.500
AND IT'S CERTAINLY NOT THE WAY

39:17.500 --> 39:19.000
I'M REALIZING I WANT TO BE

39:19.000 --> 39:21.433
LOVED.

39:21.433 --> 39:26.800
PULL OVER.

39:26.800 --> 39:28.100
YOU SHOULD THINK ABOUT WHO YOU

39:28.100 --> 39:29.133
WANT TO SPEND THE REST OF YOUR

39:29.133 --> 39:32.133
LIFE WITH AND WHY.

39:32.133 --> 39:33.867
BUT IT'S NOT ME.

39:33.867 --> 39:37.133
AND I CAN'T EVER GO BACK.

40:01.333 --> 40:03.800
>> * THIS IS THE LIFE

40:03.800 --> 40:05.400
>> HEY, WE GOT HERE AS FAST AS

40:05.400 --> 40:06.200
WE COULD.

40:06.200 --> 40:07.400
>> YEAH, WE COULDN'T HAVE YOU

40:07.400 --> 40:08.400
STANDING ON THE CORNER WEARING

40:08.400 --> 40:09.367
WHAT YOU'RE WEARING FOR TOO

40:09.367 --> 40:10.033
LONG.

40:10.033 --> 40:11.533
SOMEBODY MIGHT PUT YOU TO WORK.

40:11.533 --> 40:13.867
>> [giggles]

40:13.867 --> 40:15.700
>> PLEASE TELL ME YOU DID NOT

40:15.700 --> 40:17.267
GIVE VICTOR BACK YOUR RING.

40:17.267 --> 40:19.167
>> HELL, NO, I EARNED THIS.

40:19.167 --> 40:21.967
[laughter]

40:21.967 --> 40:23.300
>> JUST DON'T DROP IT IN MY CAR.

40:23.300 --> 40:26.333
FINDERS, KEEPERS.

40:26.333 --> 40:27.667
>> SO WHERE WE GOING, LADIES?

40:27.667 --> 40:28.533
>> WHERE ELSE?

40:28.533 --> 40:31.800
TO TEAR UP ATLANTA, TOGETHER.

40:31.800 --> 40:34.300
>> WHOO!

40:34.300 --> 40:35.133
>> * AND WE LIVE THIS

40:35.133 --> 40:36.533
* TO THE FULLEST

40:36.533 --> 40:39.300
* DO WHATEVER WE LIKE

40:44.200 --> 40:47.633
* THIS, THIS, THIS IS THE LIFE

40:47.633 --> 40:48.667
* AND WE LIVE THIS

40:51.500 --> 40:52.933
THEM $200,000.

40:52.933 --> 40:53.667
>> DAMN.

40:53.667 --> 40:55.600
I NEED MORE THAN A PAYMENT PLAN.

40:55.600 --> 40:56.767
I NEED A PRAYER.

40:56.767 --> 40:57.800
>> I KNOW HE DOES NOT HAVE OUR

40:57.800 --> 40:59.333
BABY IN MY OVERNIGHT BAG.

40:59.333 --> 41:00.567
>> YOUR BABY?

41:00.567 --> 41:01.367
>> WE ADOPTED.

41:01.367 --> 41:02.733
>> WOULD YOU MIND IF I DINED IN?

41:02.733 --> 41:03.400
>> SURE, YEAH, WE COULD JUST

41:03.400 --> 41:04.800
ORDER DELIVERY.

41:04.800 --> 41:05.667
>> THAT'S NOT WHAT I MEANT BY

41:05.667 --> 41:08.000
DINING IN.

41:08.000 --> 41:08.867
>> OH.

41:08.867 --> 41:10.133
>> * FEEL SO FREE

41:10.133 --> 41:12.200
* DON'T NEED ANYONE TO KEEP

41:12.200 --> 41:16.733
* MY MIND, MY BODY, MY SOUL

41:16.733 --> 41:20.867
* SINGLE

41:20.867 --> 41:23.133
* LADIES
